localString.value: Aggressive, nightmarish predators, Giant Spiders first trap their prey within their webs, then subdue them with poisonous venom.
A small flock of butterflies have gathered here, fluttering delicately with the breeze.
Follow the road north to Tobaro Follow the road east to Brosna
Place this object in any area where you want tracking to occur. Set Will to the DC of tracking in this area.

This house is for players to purchase and furnish. Only one player at a time can actually "own" the house, but when he or she logs off, someone else can claim it for a time. The furniture bought is saved on a deed. See a housing merchant to buy a key and furniture.
